snippet.title: TR3X PR0DÚCTÍ0NS
snippet.description:
Hello everyone, and welcome to my YouTube channel! If you like to read more about this channel, click on my about page...
----------------------
This is home to my logo content, especially the logo history series. I also do other series on this channel as well, such as TR3X Logo Reviews, TR3X Logo Lists/Compilations, Logos from [Year], TR3X Logo Evolutions, TR3X Logo Captures, etc. I have been doing this content ever since 4th June 2016, although I have been interested in logos at the start of 2012 before my YouTube account was made. If you are interested in this type of content, then remember to subscribe, and like/comment if you feel like it! Thanks for reading. :-)
-----------------------
The "T of Wonder" logo symbol was made by me back on 11th June 2017. 
The photograph in the background of my profile picture was taken by me at Ludlow on 2nd November 2019. 
The photograph featured in the channel banner was taken by me at Orleton on 5th September 2020.
